Bibarel (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0399: Bidoof
Pokémon
#0401: Kricketot →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Bibarel (TCG Pocket).

Bibarel has been featured on 10 different cards since it debuted in the Diamond & Pearl expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Bibarel cards are normally Colorless-type or Water-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Bibarel

Bibarel
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
